item.description: Contributing Guidelines Code of Conduct This project is intended to be a safe, welcoming space for collaboration. All contributors are expected to adhere to the Contributor Covenant code of conduct. Thank you for being kind to each other! Contributions welcome! Before spending lots of time on something, ask for feedback on your idea first! Please search issues and pull requests (or in any of the related projects) before adding something new!
